org.bonitasoft.engine.identity

Class RoleUpdater

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.identity.RoleUpdater
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RoleUpdater
extends Object
implements Serializable
    represents a helper for updating a Role. Chaining is possible with this updator to ease the Role update.
    For instance, new RoleUpdater("member").setDisplayName("Member").setIconName("userIcon");
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
    See Also:
    Role, Serialized Form
